import tooltip from '../tooltip'
export default {
  name: 'mu-th',
  props: {
    tooltip: {
      type: String
    },
    tooltipPosition: {
      type: String,
      default: 'bottom-right'
    },
    touch: {
      type: Boolean,
      default: false
    }
  },
  data () {
    return {
      tooltipShown: false,
      tooltipTrigger: null
    }
  },
  mounted () {
    this.tooltipTrigger = this.$refs.wrapper
  },
  computed: {
    verticalPosition () {
      const tooltipPosition = this.tooltipPosition.split('-')
      return tooltipPosition[0]
    },
    horizontalPosition () {
      const tooltipPosition = this.tooltipPosition.split('-')
      return tooltipPosition[1]
    }
  },
  methods: {
    showTooltip () {
      this.tooltipShown = true
    },
    hideTooltip () {
      this.tooltipShown = false
    }
  },
  components: {
    tooltip
  }
}
